data.description: Short Sale. Short sale - seller owes close to list price, so bank approval should not be much of a challenge. Young home loved by current owner that has been maintained in good condition and did not sustain damages from the storm. Situated on a quiet street, close to the heart of Cape Coral. The seller is ready to move and give possession.  Short Sale - approval of the owner(S) of record lender(s) may be conditioned upon the gross commission being reduced. Any reduction in gross compensation will be apportioned split equally between listing and cooperating brokers. Listing price may not be sufficient to cover all encumbrances, closing costs or other seller charges. Measurements are not guaranteed. Buyer is responsible for turning on electric / water for inspections. Buyers are responsible for clean out of remainder home contents.   Agents must utilize ShowingTime to request showing appointments.
